apps.name: Youtube (YTLitePlus)
apps.subtitle: YTLite with more features!
apps.versionDescription:
Current YouTube IPA: "19.06.2"  
Current YTLitePlus Version: "2.5"  
Current App Compatibility: "iOS/iPadOS 14.0" or later

RELEASE 19.06.2•2.5: (2024•02•17)

• Updated YTLite from "2.4.1" to "2.5"
  • Added option to always show progress bar (Overlay section)
  • Added option to disable autocaptions (Player section)
  • Added option to enable Shorts only mode (Shorts section)
  • Added option to enable Pinch gesture to enter fullscreen (Shorts section)
  • Added option that opens Shorts videos as regular videos (Shorts section)
  • Added option to hide Shorts source under channel name (Shorts section)
  • Added option to add Explore to tab bar (Tab bar section)
  • Added option to set Explore tab as startup tab (Tab bar section)
  • Added option to Copy Post Text by long tap (Other section)
  • Added option to Save Post Image by long tap (Other section)
  • Added option to Save Profile Picture by long tap (Other section)
  • Added option to Fix cover images not showing in Russia (Other section)
  • Fixed Settings crash (Thanks to [[@PoomSmart](https://github.com/PoomSmart)](https://github.com/PoomSmart))
  • Fixed black screen display if content warning was disabled
  • Fixed Shorts progress bar not showing in some cases
  • Fixed Hide Watermarks option not working
  • Improved Nav bar hiding options
  • Improved Shorts elements hiding options
  • Improved Hide tab bar labels option
  • Improved Hide search history option
  • Improved ReExplore option
  • Improved Sideloading fix, updated IAmYouTube tweak 
  
Issues in this Release:
• LowContrastMode does not work *(Compatible only with YouTube v16.46.5•v17.38.10)*
• VersionSpoofer (Lite) doesn't work with YTLite *(as the version is already spoofed by YTLite to fix YTClassicVideoQuality)*
apps.localizedDescription:
YTLite with more features! 

Supercharge your YouTube experience with +20 tweaks: 

• YTLite: Ad-blocking & background playback +50 options 
• YTUHD: Unlock 2K & 4K resolutions 
• YouPiP: Enable native Picture-in-Picture 
• YTABConfig: Control A/B testing flags 
• YouMute: Mute/unmute videos 
• DontEatMyContent: Prevent notch from covering videos 
• Return YouTube Dislikes: Reinstate dislike counts 
• iSponsorBlock: Skip sponsor ads 
• YouRememberCaption: Remember video captions 
• YTNoTracking: Disable tracking parameters 
• YTUnShorts: Remove Shorts from feed 
• YTNoCheckLocalNetwork: Disable local network permission prompt 
• BigYTMiniPlayer: Larger mini player
• YTSpeed: Add playback speeds up to 5x
• YTHoldForSpeed: Toggle speeds by holding video
• YTVideoOverlay: Add buttons to video overlay 
• YouQuality: Change video quality faster
• YTNoModernUI: Replace new UI elements 
• OLEDDarkmode: True black OLED dark mode 
• OLDDarkmode: Original grey dark mode 
• LowContrastMode: Reduce interface contrast 
• YTNoSuggestedVideo: Removes the suggested video popup when finishing a video

privacy.NSAppleMusicUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to your Apple Music library.
privacy.NSBluetoothPeripheralUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires Bluetooth access to connect with nearby peripherals.
privacy.NSCameraUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to the camera to capture photos and videos.
privacy.NSContactsUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to your contacts to help you share content with your friends.
privacy.NSLocalNetworkUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires local network access to connect and communicate with nearby devices.
privacy.NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to your location while using the app to provide personalized recommendations.
privacy.NSMicrophoneUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to your microphone to record audio.
privacy.NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription: YTLitePlus requires access to your Photo Library to save photos and videos.
